dc_title_s: Cedar County, Iowa, 1951, aerial photomosaic index

Form of individual image numbering: EB-5H-[number], EB-6H-[number], EB-7H-[number], or EB-8H-[number]."Flying completed 10-1-51" Flown by Woltz Studios, Des Moines, Iowa.
